Melt the butter, then simmer the onions in the butter until they are soft.  Add the flour and stir to make a roux.  Whisk in the milk.  Add the salt.  Simmer until it thickens, then slowly add the cheese while stirring until the cheese is completely melted into the soup.  Garnish with sliced green onion.
